{"tid":2080413,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"持有住慘情收息股既咁多位,有冇諗住以期權執番少少駛費?","createTime":"2020-06-26T11:50:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T15:19:01.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec8eac5b3f3a97c7f587f26591d8414e3f997942","tid":2080413,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"非投資建議<br />\n但與其坐晌度等番家鄉<br />\n不如用期權執少少過日晨<br />\n既然大家都有貨晌手,可以試下SHORT CALL(SC)你手上既股票<br />\nSC係乜呢<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/blog/zh/%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A-%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8-%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%8E%A9%E6%B3%95-%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyhero.com.hk%2Fblog%2Fzh%2F%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25AC%258A%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8-%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E7%258E%25A9%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E4%25BD%25A3%25E9%2587%2591&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1d4f2618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/blog/zh/%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A-%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8%E6%9C%9F%E6%AC%8A%E6%95%99%E5%AD%B8-%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-%E7%8E%A9%E6%B3%95-%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91</a><br />\n賣出認購期權<br />\n<br />\n與買入認購期權的目標相反，賣出認購期權就是希望股票現價較行使價為低。假設現價騰訊是HK$366，賣出一隻認購期權，行使價是HK$370，就會得到期權金，每股期權金的價格HK$2.5，賣出一張認購期權就會得到 HK$2.5 x 100 = HK$250 的期權金。但同時要放低按金，為日後當騰訊股價升超過HK$370行使價時，有足夠的股票賣出騰訊股份。<br />\n<br />\n假設日後騰訊升到HK$380，在到期日就要以HK$380買入騰訊股份，然後以HK$370賣出，計及收到的期權金，HK$370 &ndash; HK$380 + HK$2.5 = -HK$7.5，每股要蝕HK$7.5，每張合約要蝕 HK$7.5 x 100 = HK$750。<br />\n<br />\n而只要騰訊不斷上升，要蝕的錢會不斷上升，理論上蝕是無限，賺最多只是最初的期權金所得HK$250。<br />\n<br />\n使用有關方法，投資者普遍的心態是看淡正股後市，但又不是過度看淡，一般的看法是牛皮偏淡居多。<br />\n<br />\n看到這部份，有沒有發覺買入及賣出認購期權所賺和蝕是相對，買方的賺是賣方的蝕，賣方的蝕是買方的賺，所以期權買賣其實是買賣雙方的直接對賭。<br />\n<br />\n用最簡單既方法解釋,就係你手上既收息股,到月尾都唔升穿X價,你既期權金就袋袋平安,就算升穿左,你要俾貨人,你本身都有貨,都唔會要一大舊錢俾貨人,又或者,你可以平倉,買番一張LONG CALL,咁你都只係輸兩者期權金既差價,但就可以繼續KEEP住D貨<br />\n香港既收息股,好多都有期權買賣,可以晌度睇到查下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/Products/Listed-Derivatives/Single-Stock/Stock-Options?sc_lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkex.com.hk%2FProducts%2FListed-Derivatives%2FSingle-Stock%2FStock-Options%3Fsc_lang%3Dzh-HK&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2hyC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=44c049a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkex.com.hk/Products/Listed-Derivatives/Single-Stock/Stock-Options?sc_lang=zh-HK</a><br />\n因為大家係做SHORT,時間係對大家有利,輸既最多只係你X既價位再向上既升幅差價,但睇近期收息股既表現,大家可以自己考慮一下<br />\n睇番就算匯豐一張SC,都有幾百蚊執,好過日日睇住D股票欲哭無淚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3120c9069330fe6caf6445339ec979eff54940","tid":2080413,"uid":31060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"教一班揸住慘情收息股嘅人玩期權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好害人地d 仔女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收息股都係輸下價<br />\n期權可以輸跳樓呀"},{"pid":"f6a3a7c06bce602507190e5128d7adc73bd05fc5","tid":2080413,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3120c9069330fe6caf6445339ec979eff54940","tid":2080413,"uid":31060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"教一班揸住慘情收息股嘅人玩期權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好害人地d 仔女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收息股都係輸下價<br />\n期權可以輸跳樓呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:41:38.000Z","msg":"SC,有貨<br />\n可以輸乜?"},{"pid":"e7e58b3740087de7241a24956839a4eb673428fa","tid":2080413,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3120c9069330fe6caf6445339ec979eff54940","tid":2080413,"uid":31060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:40:14.000Z","msg":"教一班揸住慘情收息股嘅人玩期權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好害人地d 仔女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收息股都係輸下價<br />\n期權可以輸跳樓呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"再者,你買幾十張幾百張梗係可以輸跳樓啦<br />\n一張半張執幾百<br />\n點樣輸跳樓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ecc088fdbba1c5481d59e4c52fb4471249fabc","tid":2080413,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f83c4656f332e05411e219b86e5dc0158d5ce74","tid":2080413,"uid":353278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"咁少貨夠唔夠畀手續費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}